{"tid":1846673,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[扁平足絲] 求好嘅物理治療同鞋墊","createTime":"2020-01-27T16:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T11:45:51.000Z","uid":334305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"acbcf555c29cd3896b4e2f765061ca237e81b98e","tid":1846673,"uid":334305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"我扁平足都有好多年，<br />\n細細個果陣，著Dr Kong 都仲頂得信<br />\n只係行超過一個鐘會極攰<br />\n<br />\n而家一行超過一個鐘，<br />\n左腳（嚴重d果隻）就會痛到痴線，<br />\n拗哂柴咁，腳底內側一大力「禁」落去就好酸，右腳跟著就會開始奶奶地野<br />\n<br />\n早幾年，有排一行路就痛，行一步痛一步<br />\n睇家庭醫生話我足底筋膜炎（但無照x光），開左消炎藥同半年exempt pe 堂假紙比我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年開始叫做搵到少少錢，<br />\n試埋brikenstock 幾款鞋墊都覺得成效不大，都係日痛夜痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跪求好嘅<span style=\"color: green;\">治療師</span>，正正經經照返x光，同想醫好/斷尾/最少都痛少d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> budget 物理治療800蚊左右一次都afford得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋如果有d度身訂做 用開好嘅鞋墊<br />\n都想問埋邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔小心行多左痛到hihi起身開post"},{"pid":"1186fbbdcdfacf42ca9f39c5aa4071c327d8a37f","tid":1846673,"uid":127889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:54:03.000Z","msg":"叫佢REFER你去醫院啦<br />\n我好細個個陣就已比人REFER左去義肢及矯形部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ea3c924ccffceab2af9f630525d084752c740b","tid":1846673,"uid":97909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1186fbbdcdfacf42ca9f39c5aa4071c327d8a37f","tid":1846673,"uid":127889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:54:03.000Z","msg":"叫佢REFER你去醫院啦<br />\n我好細個個陣就已比人REFER左去義肢及矯形部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:58:49.000Z","msg":"<i